summary: Racemenu Preset with both HDT hair and non HDT
descriptionHtml:
So, a while back, I was creating a character, and she ended up looking a bit like Taylor Swift (Uploaded Picture to [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/images/599533/?]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/images/599533/?[/url] )  

I decided to alter it a bit more to hopefully be more accurate to Taylor Swift. Figured I may as well upload it!

She just so happens to be a Nord :)
